  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi @mverissimo, do you wrap InstantSearch widgets with `<LoadingIndicator>`? If so, you're mounting/unmounting these in an infinite loop. See [Show and hide widgets](https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/widgets/show-and-hide-widgets/react/) in our documentation for more info on how to handle mounting/unmounting widgets, for example by setting the `preserveSharedStateOnUnmount` flag in the latest version of React InstantSearch.\r\n\r\nIf your issue persists, don't hesitate to provide a reproducible sandbox.",
